description: This database contains the data from the 3rd edition of the NIST-JANAF Thermochemical Tables.

distribution.description: A zipped file of all 1,799 JANAF species, index, and definition files.
distribution.title: Compressed folder of all JANAF files

distribution.description: An index file containing metadata for each of the species, including chemical name, data file name, CAS Number (Chemical Abstracts Registry Number), molecular formula (in Hill-sorted order), and state (or phase).
distribution.title: JANAF Species Index

publisher.name: National Institute of Standards and Technology

title: NIST-JANAF Thermochemical Tables - SRD 13
